<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h2>{{appName}}</h2>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <h3>Congratulations! 🎉</h3>
    <p>Your application for the {{role}} role has been approved. You now have access to all {{role}}-specific features and capabilities.</p>
    
    <p>What's next?</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Visit your dashboard to explore your new features</li>
      <li>Complete your {{role}} profile</li>
      <li>Review the {{role}} guidelines and best practices</li>
    </ul>

    <center>
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </center>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This email was sent by {{appName}}. If you did not request this role, please contact support immediately.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 